2.3. 分页查询订单信息

URL: http://localhost:8080/app/page/{pageIndex}/{pageSize}

Type: GET

Author: yu 2018/9/4.

Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded;charset=utf-8

Description: 分页查询订单信息

Request-headers:

HeaderValueTypeRequiredDescription

token

string

false

desc

Path-parameters:

ParameterValueTypeRequiredDescription

pageIndex

int32

true

当前页码

pageSize

int32

true

页面大小

Response-fields:

FieldTypeDescriptionSince

records

array

分页数据

-

└─orderId

int32

订单id

-

└─orderType

enum

订单类型
WAIT_PAY -("0","已支付")
PAID -("1","已支付")
EXPIRED -("2","已经失效")

-

total

int64

获取总记录

-

size

int64

每页显示条数

-

count

int64

总数

-

page

int64

当前页码

-

Response-example:

{
	"records": [
		{
			"orderId": 518,
			"orderType": "WAIT_PAY"
		}
	],
	"total": 172,
	"size": 672,
	"count": 77,
	"page": 849
}

Curl-example:

curl -X GET -H 'token:kk' -i http://localhost:8080/app/page/891/10
